originalText.text: The receptionist in this office is a total ignorant idiot. Maybe she finished high school at best. I called & she booked me in for a 1pm appointment. I arrived 40 mins early & she tried to reprimand me like I was a child. THEN, on top of that. The incompetent doctor arrives almost 2 hours late claiming he had an emergency surgery to perform. Save your time & money to go find another doctor.
